    "• TCNN 14 explored CNN-rand, which uses randomly initialized word embeddings, and CNN-non-static, which uses pre-trained word embeddings.",
    "A threshold of 0.3 was set, leading to the rejection of outputs below this value for RoBERTa (Robustly Optimized BERT Pretraining Approach) 64, MT-DNN (Multi task Deep.",
